com.example.csproject.stock

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.csproject.stock.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    Object representing a user. Contains username, password, balance, and various Sets and Maps representing the user's owned stocks, watchlist, amount of stocks owned, and reminders for buying and selling those stocks.
